rComments: Professor Hassan is great! His classes are very interesting and lectures are nice to listen too. During the semester there are a few assignments but two big papers. The final is very intensive due to all of the content but overall the class is great

His lectures aren't really that useful.  The lecture notes he gives out online is all you'll need for midterms, and exams.  But if you ever have any problems, he's really easy to approch and he'll try his best to explain the topic to you.

Prof is very nice and approachable. However his class can put you to sleep. His exam is fairly easy, as he tells you what to cover. (I personally did not read the textbook and ended up with a B in his class just studying mainly lecture notes) His TA Orly.N is great! (I hope I spelled it right) Very nice and friendly as well~
it wasn't so bad, but it was kind of hard to understand him with his accent.  just read the lecture slides.  but he's fair.
